I don't know what its worth actually, something similar has been offered on ebay for quite awhile and hasnt sold at the offered price.  I can't recall what that price was, maybe search ebay for an indication of at least what price it was offered.

Actually, I knew I had seen this card before.  It has been offerred on ebay for quite a while and has not been sold at continually lowered prices.   Last time it was offered the listing was to have ended 11/17/14 but the listing was ended by the seller because the item was no longer available. That listing had a starting price of 249.99 but again it had been offered previously at much higher prices.  Maybe the seller found a buyer at or near 249.99 and pulled the card?  Since you are asking..."What's a card like this worth? Any interest?".... I assume you own it and I'd say it's worth less than 249.99.

[url]http://www.ebay.com/itm/1911-T201-Mecca-Double-Folders-Error-MISCUT-Mcginnity-Mccarty-BVG-Not-PSA-T206-/171539302044?pt=US_Baseball&hash=item27f08a069c[/url]

I've decided to keep the card...
Happy Thanksgiving
